ode> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window/load_event\"><code>load</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/message_event\"><code>message</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/messageerror_event\"><code>messageerror</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/offline_event\"><code>offline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/online_event\"><code>online</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/orientationchange_event\"><code>orientationchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/pagehide_event\"><code>pagehide</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/pageshow_event\"><code>pageshow</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/paste_event\"><code>paste</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window/popstate_event\"><code>popstate</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/rejectionhandled_event\"><code>rejectionhandled</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window/storage_event\"><code>storage</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/unhandledrejection_event\"><code>unhandledrejection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/unload_event\"><code>unload</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayactivate_event\"><code>vrdisplayactivate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayblur_event\"><code>vrdisplayblur</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayconnect_event\"><code>vrdisplayconnect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaydeactivate_event\"><code>vrdisplaydeactivate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaydisconnect_event\"><code>vrdisplaydisconnect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayfocus_event\"><code>vrdisplayfocus</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypointerrestricted_event\"><code>vrdisplaypointerrestricted</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypointerunrestricted_event\"><code>vrdisplaypointerunrestricted</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypresentchange_event\"><code>vrdisplaypresentchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herança:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Altura&nbsp;(em pixels) da janela de visualização do navegador, incluindo, se renderizado, a barra de rolagem horizontal.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\"><strong>Note:</strong> If you use <code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/XPCOM_Interface_Reference/nsIDOMWindowUtils#setCSSViewport()\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">nsIDOMWindowUtils.setCSSViewport()</a></code> to set the virtual window size for page layout purposes, the value returned by this property corresponds to the viewport height set using that method.</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <var>intViewportHeight</var> = window.innerHeight;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"Value","isH3":true,"content":"<p>On return, <code>intViewportHeight</code>&nbsp;is the height of the browser window's viewport.</p>\n\n<p>The <code>window.innerHeight</code> property is read only; it has no default value.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Notes","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <code>innerHeight</code> property is supported in any window object like a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>window</code></a>, a frame, a frameset, or a secondary window.</p>\n\n<p>There is <a class=\"link-https external\" href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=189112#c7\" rel=\" noopener\">an algorithm</a> to obtain the height of the viewport excluding, if rendered, the horizontal scrollbar.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"assuming_a_frameset","title":"Assuming a frameset","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> intFrameHeight <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHeight<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// or</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> intFrameHeight <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHeight<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// will return the height of the frame viewport within the frameset</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> intFramesetHeight <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> parent<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHeight<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// will return the height of the viewport of the closest frameset</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> intOuterFramesetHeight <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> top<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHeight<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// will return the height of the viewport of the outermost frameset</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"inlineIndicator todo todoInline\"><strong>FIXME:</strong> <em>link to an interactive demo here</em></span></p>\n\n<p>To change the size of a window, see <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/resizeBy\"><code>window.resizeBy()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> and <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/resizeTo\"><code>window.resizeTo()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>\n\n<p>To get the outer height of a window, i.e. the height of the whole browser window, see <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/outerHeight\"><code>window.outerHeight</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"graphical_example","title":"Graphical example","isH3":true,"content":"<p>The following figure shows the difference between <code>outerHeight</code> and <code>innerHeight</code>.</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"innerHeight vs outerHeight illustration\" src=\"/@api/deki/files/213/=FirefoxInnerVsOuterHeight2.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Specification","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-view/#dom-window-innerheight\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM) View Module<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'window.innerHeight' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Rascunho atual</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect4\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect5\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>1</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.7 or earlier)<sup>[1]</sup></td>\n   <td>9</td>\n   <td>9</td>\n   <td>3</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>1</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.0)<sup>[1]</sup></td>\n   <td>9</td>\n   <td>9</td>\n   <td>3</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] From Firefox 4 to 24 this property was buggy and could give a wrong value before page load on certain circumstances, see <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=641188\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug&nbsp;641188</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/innerWidth\"><code>window.innerWidth</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/outerHeight\"><code>window.outerHeight</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/outerWidth\"><code>window.outerWidth</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Notes","id":"notes"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Specification","id":"specification"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Altura (em pixels) da janela de visualização do navegador, incluindo, se renderizado, a barra de rolagem horizontal.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window.innerHeight","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"window.innerHeight","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"window.innerHeight","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Window.innerHeight","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Window.innerHeight","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Window.innerHeight","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/window/innerheight","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/window/innerheight/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window","title":"Window"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window/innerHeight","title":"Window.innerHeight"}],"pageTitle":"Window.innerHeight - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}